past two years, was ridden by Corey Nakatani, carried high weight
of 118 pounds and returned $2.40 and $2.20. Front-running Bella
Chiarra was another 5&AMP;frac34; lengths back in third in the field of seven
and was $2.80 to show.
</P>
<P>
