<HEADLINE> Mutiny 3, D.C. United 0  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   TAMPA, Fla. (AP) -- Eric Quill scored twice and Mamadou Diallo
got his league-leading 17th goal as the Tampa Bay Mutiny beat D.C.
United 3-0 Tuesday night.
</P>
<P>
   Carlos Valderrama got his 19th assist on Quill's second goal,
tying United's Marco Etcheverry for the league record.
</P>
<P>
   Valderrama found Quill splitting D.C. United's defense in the
46th minute for Tampa Bay's final goal.
</P>
<P>
